-- Bus Crash Near Padua Kills at Least Five, Ansa Says
-- B y   J e r r o l d   C o l t e n
-- 2012-05-05T09:42:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-05/bus-crash-near-padua-kills-at-least-five-ansa-says.html
At least five people were killed and
several injured when a bus carrying retired Carabinieri police
officers crashed near Padua,  Italy  this morning, Ansa news
agency reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
